iso_3166:CountrySubdivisionCodeSimpleType

simpleType CountrySubdivisionCodeSimpleType in namespace http://release.niem.gov/niem/codes/iso_3166-1/5.0/

Definition

A data type for a state, commonwealth, province, or other such geopolitical subdivision of a country. Sourced from ISO 3166 Part 2.
